Dystrack is experiencing some issues currently so how you request songs changed for now.
To request a song please pick it from this list and then ping @Dystifyzer or an active moderator on Youtube with the song. However, this only works if requests are open.
(Moderators have a blue wrench next to their name. DysBot, NightBot and DysGames can not take requests because they are not humans.)
